title: Kim Kardashian Rocks Racy Corset, Nears Wardrobe Malfunction: Pics
text: Kim Kardashian Rocks Racy Corset, Nears Wardrobe Malfunction: Pics by Antoinette Bueno 9:02 AM PST, February 23, 2017 Photo: X17online.com Kim Kardashian West is flaunting her sexy style. The 36-year-old reality superstar ensured all eyes were on her on Wednesday in Los Angeles, when she sported a skintight, white lace corset with Yeezy sweatpants. Kim's low-cut top made her dangerously close to a wardrobe malfunction, which she paired with an oversized puffer coat. Photo: X17online.com Kim sported heeled booties during her lunch outing, and accessorized with sunglasses and a yellow purse. Photo: X17online.com The Keeping Up With the Kardashians also spent Wednesday wishing her late father, Robert Kardashian, a happy birthday. The famous attorney, who died in 2003 of esophageal cancer, would have been 73 years old. "Happy Birthday dad!" Kim tweeted alongside a black-and-white throwback family pic including her mother, Kris Jenner, and siblings Kourtney, Khloe and Rob Kardashian. "I love this family photo. I love our family. Thank you for EVERYTHING. I'm so grateful you are my dad!" Happy Birthday dad! I love this family photo. I love our family. Thank you for EVERYTHING.
